        <updateDate>2008-06-17T21:00:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>10k Run for the Border Act - Amends the Immigration and Nationality Act to increase employer civil fines for: (1) hiring, or recruiting or referring for a fee, an alien that the employer knows is not authorized for employment; and (2) continuing to employ such alien.</p> <p>Sets forth a federal-state (and local) allocation of such additional penalty funds. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
